reviewText: I was a little disappointed with this one; I love Dennis Brown, and he has some amazing dvds out there that I would highly recommend....but some of the other acts in this dvd leave a lot to be desired. Everyone is wearing tuxes and fancy duds, but if you put lipstick on a pig....it's still a pig. Probably wouldn't recommend this particular one, unless you want to take a nap while it's playing.
